Quantity makes approx 4* pancakes (good for 1* person)
                                   Mash 1* ripe banana
                                   Add 2* eggs and beat together
                                   Add about 0.5* cup almond meal
                                   Add a few spoons of ground up seeds or powders (hemp / flaxseed / linseed etc)
                                   Mix it all really well
                                   Add a handful of berries (optional, and can be frozen)
                                   Fry
